SQL考点总结
  1.建表
    creat table xx(
      xx integer/varchar    primary key/unique/references xx,
    )
  2.建视图
    creat view as xx
      select
      from
      where xx is null
  3.基本语句
    *基本SFW
    *extract(year from current_date)
  4.求'数量die Anzahl der Kunden'同时满足其他条件'mehr als xx'
    注意顺序 SFWGHO
    select count(xx)
    from xxxxxxxx
    group by xx
    having count(xxxx)>xx
  5.找到满足'最大数量die meisten Kunden'的'地点ort'
    select ort
    from xxxxxxxx
    group by ort
    having count(*)>=all(
      select count(*)
      from xxxxxxxx
      group by ort
    )
  6.更新表的内容'setzen xxxx ein'
    update xxxx set xx=(
      SFW
    )
  7.合并操作'mengenbasierte Operation'
    SFW
    intersect
    SFW
  8.命名及from里面内容的修改'Differenz der A und B'
    select xx,A-B
    from (select xx,xxx as A
          FW)
          natural join
          (select xx,xxx as B
          FW)
